<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.3">
<l>aṉṉē yivarai yaṟivaṉ maṟaināṉkum</l>
<l>muṉṉē yuraitta muṉiva rivarvantu</l>
<l>poṉṉēy vaḷaikavarntu pōkār maṉampukun</l>
<l>teṉṉē yivareṇṇu meṇṇa maṟiyōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh, wonder! I know him. He is the sage who long ago</l>
<l>Proclaimed the four Vedas. Having come [here],</l>
<l>Snatching my gold-like bangles, entering my heart,</l>
<l>He does not leave. What are the thoughts he is thinking? We do not know.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
